{"tid":2015850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍驅逐艦駛經台海　2轟炸機飛近台灣","createTime":"2020-05-14T03:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T07:32:44.000Z","uid":95138,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b65a81c95b81445aa2faa4ba9fd1c5ba4cfda1d6","tid":2015850,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T03:51:11.000Z","msg":"美國海軍太平洋艦隊表示，驅逐艦麥坎貝爾號周四（14日）早上由北向南駛經台灣海峽，前往印太海域執行一般航行任務。台灣的國防部同日證實美軍有關行動。與此同時，美軍兩架B1B戰略轟炸機亦飛近台灣。<br />\n<br />\n台國防部的新聞稿指出，美軍一艘作戰艦當日駛經台灣海峽，執行一般航行任務，之後繼續向南航行，台軍方運用聯合情監偵掌握區域情勢，狀況正常。據台國防部統計，今次是美國軍艦本年以來第6次通過台灣海峽，對上一次是在4月24日的驅逐艦巴里號；而去年美國軍艦則9度通過台灣海峽。<br />\n<br />\n美軍太平洋艦隊亦在Facebook主動公開今次航行情況，隸屬第15驅逐艦中隊的麥坎貝爾號駛經台灣海峽。照片可見，水兵在艦上監察情況，期間一架MH60海鷹直升機從甲板升空。<br />\n<br />\n另有消息指，美軍兩架B1B戰略轟炸機從關島安德森空軍基地，經台灣東面海域飛向西北方向。兩架支援的KC135加油機為B1B轟炸機空中加油後，則飛返安德森空軍基地。"},{"pid":"daca8a203a04e3bdd0e47c58f0076d1a2b1f7004","tid":2015850,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7FwKsO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7FwKsO.jpg&h=d8edea95&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5rTdk8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5rTdk8.jpg&h=96b19c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OijJAzs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOijJAzs.jpg&h=0b5d51cd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q7rjTk6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq7rjTk6.jpg&h=0fb5bffa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a58224d33b64b93ad1b9acc4418c876c6a9b5ccc","tid":2015850,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yJQArHV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyJQArHV.jpg&h=22f2d1e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbi